{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"caa48e9d-7864-44b9-b8ce-76a8a737bca6","content":"Here's what you need to do:\n\n1. **Update package references** in your `.csproj`:\n   ```xml\n   <!-- Remove -->\n   <PackageReference Include=\"xunit.runner.visualstudio\" Version=\"...\" />\n\n   <!-- Add -->\n   <PackageReference Include=\"xunit.v3.runner.mtp\" Version=\"1.*\" />\n   ```\n\n2. **Upgrade xUnit** — MTP requires **xUnit v3**. Replace:\n   ```xml\n   <!-- Remove -->\n   <PackageReference Include=\"xunit\" Version=\"2.9.3\" />\n\n   <!-- Add -->\n   <PackageReference Include=\"xunit.v3\" Version=\"1.*\" />\n   ```\n\n3. **Add the MTP property** to your `.csproj`:\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n\n4. **Fix breaking changes** from xUnit v2 → v3:\n   - Namespace: `Xunit` → `Xunit` (mostly the same, but some types moved)\n   - `[Fact]` and `[Theory]` still work\n   - `Assert` API is largely compatible, but some overloads changed\n   - `IClassFixture<T>` / `ICollectionFixture<T>` still work\n   - **`Task`-based async** is preferred; `async void` tests are no longer supported\n\n5. **Run tests** with:\n   ```bash\n   dotnet test\n   ```\n   Or run the test project directly (MTP makes it an executable):\n   ```bash\n   dotnet run --project YourTests.csproj\n   ```\n\n**Key point:** You cannot use MTP with xUnit v2 — the migration to v3 is required. Check the [xUnit v3 migration guide](https://xunit.net/docs/v3-migration) for a full list of breaking changes.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"ac4ee152-957c-44ae-b1b5-27deb69b15c9","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user wants to migrate their xUnit.net project from VSTest (using xunit.runner.visualstudio) to Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP). Let me provide a concise answer based on my knowledge of this migration path.","outputTokens":544,"requestId":"7C2F:8224F:25D7A3C:29DAC86:69F93E21"},"id":"2eafec15-df08-43bf-94da-37f844b25b40","timestamp":"2026-05-05T00:47:42.222Z","parentId":"6e9700be-ed6d-4399-b745-95941fae611f"}
